<I>This is, of course, assuming the caster isnt afraid of the /pet back off key (which he shouldnt be...backing off a pet often is 99% of pet control in a group with an enchanter). But if he isnt you can do a couple of things..<P>1) stun and blanket, if you have it memed.<BR>or<BR>2) aggro the mob...move it away from the group, and root/slow it. Who gives a **** if the pet takes some damage....just dont let it beat on you or the cleric for very long =D.<P></I><P>3.  Cast invis on pet owner  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">
