<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Last night I had my first run at KC, at Level 45.  I tried once yelling for a group, no answer, went to BW for a bit and got bored.  when the group in BW broke I went back to KC and yelled again.  I was invited to a group where all were 50+.  <P>I was told I couldn't mez anything because of my level but could try if I wanted once or twice, the cleric would keep an eye on me.<P>We were at right moat and got 1 or 2 wanderers and some multipule pulls.  All my mezes stuck and I was more than a mana battery.  We moved in to left room when it opened and continued.<P>It was a blast, there'd be some times where it was just one after another, and times where I was constantly running 1-2.5m.<P>Our tank was amazingly competant, asking in group mode which target next, actually pausing instead of just rushing to the next one.  The other tanks just took queue from him.  <P>At the worse times we'd have ppl running through the room pulling from upstairs and their mobs would agro our medders. At one point I had 4 skels and a dog mez'd while the tanks and air pet just ripped through the targets one at at time pretty quick.<P>The mage did a pretty good job of pulling his pet off but one time it did get "stuck" on the mob.  I told him to back it off again and hit color shift.  Got the pet enough time to back up and I rooted the mob so it couldn't reach the pet, all went well.<P>In the course of the night 3 people died, the cleric once and me twice.<P>Both times I went down was after extended agroing from pullers (no-one was ks'ing) and I was 0m.  The cleric and I were oom so I tashed 2 mobs and tried to run them to an unoccupied room, knowing I was going down, announcing to the group what I was doing and where so they could be aware.<P>Both times I got a 49+ rez from the ingroup cleric and we were back in action as soon as I was 1m and shielded.<P>Overall, I got 2yellow bubs through the night, made some friends, got put on some friends lists and had an absolute blast.  I'd have gotten more exp in BW helping a Wiz Quad, which is pretty regular invite for me but it was no-where near as fun.<P>This was a pickup group that formed and had 3 of the original, from when I got there, members leave and replacements leave a few times.<P>It was though an absolute blast.<P>If anyone's in a good dungeon and needs a chanter on Fennin, Give me a poke.<P>  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>Blurem<BR>  Level 52 Enchanter of Fennin Ro
</FONT>
